original_title: Keighley & Worth Valley Railway – Diesel & Mixed Traffic Gala 2021
overview: This 3 disc set sees us visit the Keighley and Worth Valley Railway for their Diesel and Mixed Traffic Gala in September 2021.  The running time for this set around 3 hours spread across 3 discs, and features a number of locations and onboard footage.
title: Keighley & Worth Valley Railway – Diesel & Mixed Traffic Gala 2021
